    public class ThyConverterImpl<TBus extends BaseAclfBus<?,?>>
extends BaseConverterImpl<TBus>
implements ThyConverter<TBus>
    An implementation of the model object 'Thy Converter'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Firing Ang
    • Firing Ang Limit
    • NBridges
    • Idc
    • Dc Voltage
    • Power Demand
    • Power Factor Angle
    • Ac Rated Voltage
    • Dc Base Voltage
    • Commuting Z
    • Xformer Ratio
    • Xformer Tap Setting
    • Xformer Tap Step Size
    • Xformer Tap Limit
    • Commuting Capacitor
    • Xfr From Id
    • Xfr To Id
    • Xfr Cir Id

      • solveRectifier

        public void solveRectifier()
        Solve the rectifier firing angle alpha, the default control mode is constant current control mode. If constant current mode cannot be maintain, it can be switched to constant ignition angle control mode

      • solveInverter

        public void solveInverter()
        Solve the inverter firing angle gamma, the default control mode is voltage control mode, maintain the dc scheduled compounded voltage change changing the firing angle gamma, if the dc voltage is gamma of the limit, adjust the tap to maintain the dc voltage within the limit
